{"tid":2363372,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【佬訊專欄】台慶未死 轉用Signal - 佬訊","createTime":"2021-01-12T07:06:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T07:38:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"38c78e3e1a241c27b73ccd168b5f463ceb473073","tid":2363372,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T07:06:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210112/GWVTCULZJREQPAUUJX4ELTJEEY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210112%2FGWVTCULZJREQPAUUJX4ELTJEEY%2F&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJuRVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=dc7f2af7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210112%2FGWVTCULZJREQPAUUJX4ELTJEEY%2F&h=cf2ab84a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210112/GWVTCULZJREQPAUUJX4ELTJEEY/</a><br />\n<br />\n【佬訊專欄】台慶未死 轉用Signal - 佬訊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bV7zHXhi_fuOKCVscTysZk-zwmw=/4800x3200/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PMCZB7JNP5DN7EMEYTE5CDJ4B4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbV7zHXhi_fuOKCVscTysZk-zwmw%3D%2F4800x3200%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPMCZB7JNP5DN7EMEYTE5CDJ4B4.JPG&h=b251b418&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Signal Wong拿視帝，就是TVB叫大家轉用Signal的首部曲。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n很多人都不知道前晚是TVB台慶，佬編也一樣，但如果你因此說台慶已死，請恕我不能夠認同。<br />\n<br />\n如果你說台慶沒有了、死了，是因為你不喜歡TVB，我覺得很難接受。甚麼叫做「死」，我們可以研究。死者倘不埋在活人的心中，那才真的死掉。反過來說，要等所有人心裏都沒有台慶，才可以說台慶已死。<br />\n<br />\n根據不正式觀察，前晚台慶差點就死了。本來在床上碌了一整晚電話，都沒有半點關於台慶的消息，到差不多11點，突然有個post彈了出來，說王浩信拿視帝多謝Yoyo。資訊膨脹，光陰有限，感激那個page的通知之餘，也默默地按了unfollow。佬編雖然冇睇，但敢肯定，前晚的台慶與過去十多年來的一樣，一定保持一貫水準。<br />\n<br />\n就像TVB劇集一定有烏溪沙青年新村，一定有都爹利街樓梯，一定有愛丁堡廣場行人隧道；前晚的台慶，想必也一如以往，有男藝人與奇怪西裝，有女藝人與低胸晚裝，有一堆大家早已沒有睇的劇集，還有植入式炸雞廣告。很多人的生活一樣是日日如是，千篇一律，難道你又能說他們死了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n還有一個秘密，佬編本來不應該說，說出來會折壽的：TVB不止前線黃，連高層也很黃。不信？看看昨晚是誰拿視帝吧。王浩信，Signal Wong, yeah you got it baby。<br />\n<br />\n放棄WhatsApp，轉用Signal，相信也不用再解釋。Signal Wong拿視帝，就是TVB叫大家轉用Signal的首部曲。<br />\n<br />\n以後邊個再講台慶已死，over my dead body。<br />\n<br />\n佬訊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/loshunhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Floshunhk%2F&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJuRVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=f4ddbb69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/loshunhk/</a>"},{"pid":"264011966ec2e2289035e7531c5abbab643c6592","tid":2363372,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T07:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf9d148acab2e432c1813c87686f2a7df33225c","tid":2363372,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T07:38:23.000Z","msg":"死者倘不埋在活人的心中，那才真的死掉。反過來說，要等所有人心裏都沒有台慶，才可以說台慶已死。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}